talent.description: I'm a chill Alpaca Vtuber! I'm a variety streamer, and do everything from gaming to art, to chatting, to ASMR, depending on how I feel!

Hi Hi! I'm your crossdressing airsoft captain, Kota Kotonya! ♥️

When I'm not on the airsoft field, I'm letting my creativity flow with some graphic design. I enjoy playing rhythm games (especially mobile ones) and chatting with my Klaw Squad! I look forward to growing by your side, teammate~
